---
title: BBQ-Sauced Chicken with Garlic Toasts and Dilly Coleslaw
description: Indulge in our BBQ-sauced chicken delight! Juicy chicken smothered in tangy BBQ sauce, paired with zesty dill coleslaw, and served with toasted garlic bread buns. This mouthwatering combo of flavours and textures is sure to make every bite a fun and delicious experience!

